Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.89,0:00:17.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.85,0:00:21.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据来报称  达尔塔尼亚太子萨义德阁下暴毙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎阁下继承了他的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.44,0:00:30.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就表示米尔扎阁下没有背弃誓约啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.90,0:00:33.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.28,0:00:34.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟译尔玛大人的占卜结果一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德军攻过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现包召唤了雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还用荆棘藏住了通往村子的路.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.19,0:02:34.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只需让瓦尔林德骑士团直接前往那小子的城即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.91,0:02:38.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的职责是当胆小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在他们后面  决不能看丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过即使有机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也决不能发动进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.67,0:02:46.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,吉德  福林德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接不来大伙就交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然说起这话了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.15,0:03:06.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我早晚会出去找迪米特里耶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到今天为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的表妹穿过德尼尔加进军已有七天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.41,0:03:19.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在附近扎营之后便再无动作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.00,0:03:22.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说不知道今后会有什么动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过先向莱加里亚伯爵赛尔杰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.71,0:03:28.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及基尔希斯王索伦请求援军吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,至于哈曼的女王艾德吉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就让她派出海洋宫殿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.05,0:03:35.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.05,0:03:40.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是治理塞维斯和弗维斯的披席克阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,替我带个话 让他发兵进攻奥赛尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一味地挨打可不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他尽情大闹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对永夜之森的提欧•科尔内罗有什么安排吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.87,0:04:00.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁塔巴正在朝提欧的城进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.25,0:04:04.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就告诉他 让他与那边的敌军交战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.17,0:04:12.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我仅率领骑兵去找维拉尔哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伊戈尔你就率领步兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.72,0:04:16.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在我后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 兄长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.27,0:04:24.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只率领骑兵赶去也帮不上维拉尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不要急躁  先等索伦大人的援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,集结好兵力再前去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.61,0:04:32.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会发生什么才叫战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果维拉尔哥哥有什么三长两短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等于葬送莱加里亚不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是葬送联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:44.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻出发  向阿尔图克全速进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被抛下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢艾莱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是兄长的契约魔法师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.68,0:05:05.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,赛尔杰大人根本不听我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.39,0:05:09.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长太害怕失去维拉尔大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.98,0:05:14.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟赛尔杰大人很崇拜维拉尔大人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,估计无法保持冷静吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会闯什么祸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.20,0:05:22.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你这么想赶紧追上去如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是赛尔杰大人有什么三长两短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.62,0:05:30.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就得找新的签约对象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.93,0:05:45.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.19,0:05:51.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔大人发来了援军的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是说想让我方派出海军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,派海军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以派遣军队对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.37,0:06:06.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,除了那个我方海军就没军舰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一搜就够了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只需向敌人的船团发射砂石炮就够了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 约希姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会上阵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.05,0:06:22.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我那些宝贝男人们一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,列队就交给你了优尔格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:31.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.77,0:06:39.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位  为了拯救危难中的维拉尔阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接下来将前往阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来举杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.58,0:06:48.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一杯麦酒将转变为战场的活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能赋予我们舒心的激昂感和勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,尔等是这场战争的主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,索伦阁下  如果我死了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能证明你是配角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.76,0:07:06.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.44,0:07:13.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后戴上面具吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,尔等扮演的是无敌勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.57,0:07:20.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,任何箭矢  任何利刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都伤不到尔等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  这场战斗究竟会变成喜剧还是悲剧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前去拉开序幕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉开序幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁塔巴军有五干士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我方的邪纹使倒是到齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然而只有两百上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我在永夜之森的集落颁布了征兵令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过至于有多少人肯来就不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还是守城好些吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能把这里变成战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就出击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着布鲁塔巴军还没进入永夜之森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了出击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:46.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告称  东南海域有船团正在逼近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.99,0:08:47.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,船团？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是哪里的船团吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是达尔塔尼亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说  米尔扎太子派员军来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  有点快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,传告提督 让那边进入警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.51,0:09:10.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  科林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,保险起见  能不能准备好镜子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一趟码头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,玛格丽特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总算见到您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.80,0:09:49.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎投靠同盟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他杀害了表示反对的父亲萨伊德大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还把不服从的部族全部歼灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.93,0:09:56.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太惊人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.77,0:10:01.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来米尔扎阁下对我失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.11,0:10:06.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我表妹是在等米尔扎阁下前去会合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.50,0:10:26.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我的圣印可不是那么容易夺走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲萨伊德・库切斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在王座上无所作为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这没远见的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有野心之人给我退场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真有种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给我逼近敌船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算船桨断了也在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一艘达尔塔尼亚的船正在高速逼近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…米尔扎・库切斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.03,0:12:17.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人从船上撤离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想弃船吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能拉你陪葬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.92,0:12:37.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是沉了这艘船吗这根本不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.68,0:12:43.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我可不会死在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.98,0:12:45.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,稳固防守争取时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.07,0:12:54.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这战斗方式实在符合阿尔图克的君主作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…名不虚传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该撤了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,友军从西南方向回撤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备攻击追兵提供掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,起火吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.21,0:13:47.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军陷入了混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请包围起来一举歼灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真变成敌人才发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克比想象中难缠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备返回战场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去追阿尔图克的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.53,0:14:25.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就接受命运灭亡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎阁下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.46,0:14:33.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟他是能凭一己之力改变战局的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.46,0:14:41.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之只要杀掉米尔扎阁下即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.76,0:14:42.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.47,0:14:46.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚便会恢复成我们的盟友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等他下次出现在战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就上阵好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因他一人失去宝贵的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可于心不忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.65,0:14:59.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,届时请允许我一同上阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是船还是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会用业火烧尽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.49,0:15:08.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚不是你的故乡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.95,0:15:12.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的部族被那男的消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.54,0:15:18.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我已经不属于魔法师协会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以随心所欲地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.30,0:15:23.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.44,0:15:38.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟出城时相比 兵力差不多翻了一倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说颁布了征兵令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真没想到能征到这么多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其实提欧大人很受爱戴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你也知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算上去搭话也不回话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,赶人的视线刺得我很疼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直对他们置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人却不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.43,0:16:06.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许只是看着就算统治了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就目前的战局来看我军处于优势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.27,0:16:15.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等到明天 哈曼的巨型船海洋宫殿也将抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:19.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德似乎直到最后都没有动作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.03,0:16:21.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.49,0:16:26.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过必须把能打的牌都打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.59,0:16:46.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌  没那么容易命中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,第一轮射击准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,通知所有船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用小型船上海滩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把尽可能多的士兵和物资运上路地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就只有莱加里亚伯爵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把人找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你一个人冲得太靠前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.86,0:17:42.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 想想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才已经向索伦大人请求增援了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.99,0:17:51.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟被瓦尔林德军包围了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,至于来不来得了就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,发现敌军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,索伦阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,莱加里亚伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,索伦阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给二位找马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.98,0:18:19.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您可是对我有大恩的维拉尔大人的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能让您死在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.23,0:18:26.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 请逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,莱加里亚伯爵逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.04,0:18:41.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我军正在跟前来增援的基尔希斯剧场王交战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.46,0:18:42.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对方很难缠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.96,0:18:46.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,断掉基尔希斯军的退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要击败敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫索伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能在此跟名震天下的瓦尔林德军厮杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是至高无上的喜悦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来堂堂正正地决胜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.85,0:19:01.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从两侧包围基尔希斯军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔希斯军的抵抗非常顽强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的战况很胶着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,派出增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把对方的兵力赶到一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.43,0:19:43.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,名震天下的重装骑士他登场了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被彻底包围了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有退路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有逃掉的体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有战斗的体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位摆好原阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.88,0:20:08.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报告 关于我军与基尔希斯军的战斗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才终于分出胜负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.47,0:20:20.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我军也有重大伤亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 因重装骑士团的活跃表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经基尔希斯军歼灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,尔等才是真正的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.65,0:20:33.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,离开不完美的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一同启程前往理想的世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.54,0:20:43.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据称基尔希斯王索伦也被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生至此闭幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.94,0:22:35.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,索伦阁下他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据称拉席克阁下逼迫奥赛尔军投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.49,0:22:44.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下也击退了布鲁塔巴军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.49,0:22:46.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克阁下倒是跟预期的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.70,0:22:49.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧真是让人吃惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.04,0:22:53.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭那点士兵 究竟是怎样击退布鲁塔巴军的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.92,0:22:57.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该向他们下达怎样的指令呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就转告他们让他们各自进攻敌阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.22,0:23:05.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦失去从属国奥赛尔和布鲁塔巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.93,0:23:09.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那瓦尔林德就只能进攻阿尔图克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.77,0:23:11.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必攻势会很猛烈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.02,0:23:14.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算城门被攻破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.94,0:23:16.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.73,0:23:20.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在必须摆脱这个困境
